<HEAD>Customs Stops Briton, Brazilian Traveling with Gold Belt</HEAD>
<DATELINE>CAIRO, Egypt (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Customs officials stopped a Briton and his
Brazilian wife after finding a solid gold belt worth $46,000 in a
